## Overview
**Adebayo ("Bayo") Ogunlesi** is a Nigerian-born lawyer, investment banker, and businessman known for his influential career in global finance and infrastructure. He is the founder and chairman of **Global Infrastructure Partners (GIP)**, a leading private equity firm specializing in infrastructure investments worldwide. In 2025, Ogunlesi joined **OpenAI’s Board of Directors**, bringing his strategic expertise to the AI sector.

